{"tid":1954082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有市民唱K到關門一刻　有麻雀館負責人指措施倉促不合理","createTime":"2020-04-01T14:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T15:13:32.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e855c142e33f61888c39c2c3a711d75f1361e103","tid":1954082,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"政府公布卡拉OK、麻雀館及夜總會，傍晚6時起要暫停營業，為期14日。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有市民在卡拉OK唱到關門前一刻</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，表示不擔心受感染。亦有市民認為政府的措施來得太遲。<br />\n<br />\n有麻雀館負責人批評，政府沒有事前通知，措施突然生效，業界無時間準備，很不合理，要求政府抗疫基金提供支援。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518300-20200401.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518300-20200401.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=31b164e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518300-20200401.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7b2c9e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518300-20200401.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dd93855a9a9ec035123b0476dcf333047ac836d7","tid":1954082,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭，入嚟睇下可以點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"877e9ae7279fb8f80434f37c44ca10671143e291","tid":1954082,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想要抗爭型立法會議員？投票啦！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n畀2020年立法會選舉候選人嘅「五大訴求」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1944136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1944136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},